Clone Terraform Repo On Local System
Copy this url
https://github.com/asecurityguru/terraform-ec2-jenkins-aws-k8s-infra-creation.git
Go to your local disk and create a folder. Example: aws_terraform_infra
In the folder, click with the right button of your mouse and select GIT BASH HERE command
On the GIT terminal write:
git clone, and paste https://github.com/asecurityguru/terraform-ec2-jenkins-aws-k8s-infra-creation.git

Open Visual Studio Code
Go to File, select open folder, and select the folder youÂ´ve created before. Example: aws_terraform_infra
And click on Open File

